    'projects.github': 'GitHub →',
    'projects.stars': 'stars',
    'projects.p1.desc': 'A NestJS REST API using MongoDB, Redis and Kafka, fully Dockerized. A deep-dive on clean, event-driven service design.',
    'projects.p2.desc': 'Community platform for the Brazilian and Portuguese Arena Breakout Infinite scene, with ammo charts, a forum and Discord connections.',
    'projects.p3.desc': 'One-command Valheim dedicated server with uMod, packaged for Pterodactyl. Game-server tooling for the long tail.',
    'projects.p4.desc': 'A drop-in upload button with built-in image cropping, rotate and zoom. Small, focused, reusable.',
    'projects.p5.desc': 'An anti-vibe-coding, agentic AI workflow that brings engineering rigor to any project, language or framework. Model-agnostic, with a native Cursor plugin.',
    'projects.p6.desc': 'A C# Oxide plugin that lets players clear items from specific inventory sections. Small utility, people actually use it.',
    'projects.p7.desc': 'Teams-first multi-agent orchestration layer for Claude Code. I contributed skill improvements, hooks, and workflow integrations.',
    'projects.p8.desc': 'A Rust CLI proxy that cuts LLM token usage by 60-90% on common dev commands. Single binary, zero dependencies.',

